MTN Offers $600 Million for 60% Stake in Zimbabwe’s Net*One, Times Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-04-18T13:50:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/mtn-offers-600-million-for-zimbabwe-s-net-one-times-reports.html
MTN Group Ltd. (MTN)  has offered $600
million for a 60 percent stake in  Zimbabwe ’s Net*One mobile
phone company,  South Africa ’s Times reported, citing
unidentified people with knowledge of the talks.    Local laws could preclude MTN from acquiring a stake of
more than 49 percent, the Johannesburg-based newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
